@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mxcvvp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (0.46 * ((v2 + 0.85 - v1 + 0.18) - wp.cos(v0 + 0.48)))
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.abs((v1 + 0.47 - tmp + 0.16)))
    v0 = ((0.98 * (v2 + 0.45 * v2 + 0.64)) / (wp.exp(v2 + 0.11) / 0.24))
    tmp = (0.11 - (0.79 + (v1 + 0.45 * v0 + 0.46)))
    data[tid] = v0
